{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"vwa.la help","description":"Everything you need to know about the vwa.la influencer marketing platform."}},"ghostPost":{"title":"Slack","slug":"slack","featured":false,"feature_image":"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/09/slack.png","created_at_pretty":"13 September, 2018","published_at_pretty":"07 August, 2018","updated_at_pretty":"02 November, 2018","created_at":"2018-09-13T20:31:26.000+00:00","published_at":"2018-08-07T20:33:00.000+00:00","updated_at":"2018-11-02T08:07:45.000+00:00","excerpt":"Ghost comes with a built-in Slack integration that allows you to notify your team any time a new post is published on your site!","meta_title":null,"meta_description":"A built-in Slack integration allows you to ensure your team is always up to date with the latest posts on your Ghost publication. Find out more üëâ‚ö°Ô∏è","og_description":null,"og_image":null,"og_title":null,"twitter_description":null,"twitter_image":null,"twitter_title":null,"authors":[{"name":"Kym Ellis","slug":"kym","bio":"Technical marketing lead","profile_image":"//www.gravatar.com/avatar/65b8e98952305f0ae0f90c7439718680?s=250&d=mm&r=x","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":null}],"primary_author":{"name":"Kym Ellis","slug":"kym","bio":"Technical marketing lead","profile_image":"//www.gravatar.com/avatar/65b8e98952305f0ae0f90c7439718680?s=250&d=mm&r=x","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":null},"primary_tag":{"name":"Community","slug":"community","description":null,"feature_image":null,"meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},"tags":[{"name":"Community","slug":"community","description":null,"feature_image":null,"meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},{"name":"#integration","slug":"hash-integration","description":null,"feature_image":null,"meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"internal"}],"plaintext":"Notify Slack when a new post is published so everyone knows when new content\ngoes live and your team stays in sync\n\nCreate a new incoming webhook in Slack\nFirst, you'll need to set up a new incoming webhook\n[https://my.slack.com/apps/new/A0F7XDUAZ-incoming-webhooks]  in your team's\nSlack configuration. An incoming webhook is a method for Slack to receive\nincoming messages to be posted to your Slack team from external services.\n\nCustomise webhook & copy URL\nOnce the webhook is created, you can optionally customise the channel, name, and\nicon which the webhook uses whenever it posts a new message. Either way,\nhowever, you'll need to copy the Webhook URL  at the very top.\n\nAdd your Slack webhook to Ghost\nInside Ghost Admin, head over to the Integrations  page and click on the Slack\nintegration settings. Here, you can paste your webhook URL, save the settings,\nand you're all done! You can also hit the green test button to make sure\neverything is working correctly with a test notification.\n\nFrom here on, your team will receive Slack notifications each time a new post is\npublished on your site üéâ\n\nMore automation with Zapier\nYou can also go further and connect other popular Ghost integrations to your\nSlack team using Zapier - so you get an overview of new comments, subscribers or\ncontact form submissions right in your workspace.","html":"<p>Notify Slack when a new post is published so everyone knows when new content goes live and your team stays in sync</p><h2 id=\"create-a-new-incoming-webhook-in-slack\">Create a new incoming webhook in Slack</h2><p>First, you'll need to set up a new <a href=\"https://my.slack.com/apps/new/A0F7XDUAZ-incoming-webhooks\">incoming webhook</a> in your team's Slack configuration. An incoming webhook is a method for Slack to receive incoming messages to be posted to your Slack team from external services.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/10/image-18.png\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><h2 id=\"customise-webhook-copy-url\">Customise webhook &amp; copy URL</h2><p>Once the webhook is created, you can optionally customise the channel, name, and icon which the webhook uses whenever it posts a new message. Either way, however, you'll need to copy the <code>Webhook URL</code> at the very top.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/10/image-19.png\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><h2 id=\"add-your-slack-webhook-to-ghost\">Add your Slack webhook to Ghost</h2><p>Inside Ghost Admin, head over to the <strong>Integrations</strong> page and click on the Slack integration settings. Here, you can paste your webhook URL, save the settings, and you're all done! You can also hit the green test button to make sure everything is working correctly with a test notification.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/10/Slack-integration.png\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><p>From here on, your team will receive Slack notifications each time a new post is published on your site üéâ</p><h2 id=\"more-automation-with-zapier\">More automation with Zapier</h2><p>You can also go further and connect other popular Ghost integrations to your Slack team using Zapier - so you get an overview of new comments, subscribers or contact form submissions right in your workspace.</p><div id=\"zap\" class=\"zapier\">\n    <script src=\"https://zapier.com/apps/embed/widget.js?services=disqus,slack&limit=2&html_id=zap\"></script>\n</div><div id=\"zap2\" class=\"zapier\">\n    <script src=\"https://zapier.com/apps/embed/widget.js?services=mailchimp,slack&limit=2&html_id=zap2\"></script>\n</div><div id=\"zap3\" class=\"zapier\">\n    <script src=\"https://zapier.com/apps/embed/widget.js?services=typeform,slack&limit=2&html_id=zap3\"></script>\n</div>","custom_template":null,"url":"https://docs.ghost.io/slack/","uuid":"2aabd66e-02c6-419d-aad5-e60b6b6ecad9","page":false,"codeinjection_foot":"","codeinjection_head":"","comment_id":"5b9ac91e3736ef00c0de3928"},"file":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":30,"height":30,"src":"/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/2682d/integration-icon.png","srcSet":"/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/2682d/integration-icon.png 1x,\n/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/0b300/integration-icon.png 1.5x,\n/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/5d50f/integration-icon.png 2x,\n/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/95621/integration-icon.png 3x"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"slack","relatedPosts":[{"node":{"slug":"custom-integrations","title":"Custom","url":"/integrations/custom-integrations/","published_at":"2018-11-11T09:07:55.000+00:00","feature_image":"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/11/custom.svg","tags":[{"slug":"utility","name":"Utility","description":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"feature_image":null},{"slug":"automation","name":"Automation","description":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"feature_image":null},{"slug":"content","name":"Content","description":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"feature_image":null},{"slug":"marketing","name":"Marketing","description":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"feature_image":null},{"slug":"email","name":"Email","description":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"feature_image":null},{"slug":"analytics","name":"Analytics","description":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"feature_image":null},{"slug":"storage","name":"Storage","description":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"feature_image":null},{"slug":"community","name":"Community","description":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"feature_image":null},{"slug":"surveys-forms","name":"Surveys & Forms","description":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"feature_image":null},{"slug":"seo","name":"SEO","description":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"feature_image":null}